name: Besiegt (Undone)
description:
This is the planar version of my Dome NFT Short Film submission for "Domance", a lyric video designed to be projected in a dome. I will gladly give HQ versions of this video, the dome-formatted video, and the Jör9 EP in whatever audio format you prefer.

The song is from the Jör9 EP, track 3 - "Besiegt (Undone)".

The sound of 1517, a hint of ancient techno influence with slower tempos (111-130bpm)
